{"tid":615761,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[嘩點鬥]17-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃8強首回合投選專區 #新垣結衣 朱千雪 姬嘉澤 周子瑜","createTime":"2018-04-03T15:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T14:08:08.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1823e4ad1280fe7b09a2aed5d05ec2717a9ac6","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣 v 朱千雪<br />\nGal Gadot v 周子瑜@TWICE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33373250814a94c487ea63a12edda1de42f31ed2","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":109,"dislike":46,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃8強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-4 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HIUU4il.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHIUU4il.png&h=1decc683&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2ikrGhT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2ikrGhT.png&h=9858f9f6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" />新垣結衣 v 朱千雪<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0Q6FBnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Q6FBnk.png&h=d7f5937a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"691fc5da62f30512dc83146ed83dd6212db72404","tid":615761,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"快D快D"},{"pid":"b7264707c70f4b9285c88121555b6b4d66bb1902","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":44,"dislike":77,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-4 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4xA95hR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4xA95hR.png&h=3ab73c0f&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DYoMUFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDYoMUFh.png&h=8e122659&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8O41HKp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8O41HKp.png&h=66d92b33&s={SIZE}\" />Gal Gadot v 周子瑜@TWICE<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/c4H073L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc4H073L.png&h=24615d99&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"af0cc3706bc9525972eb47f892d878b454350bff","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"691fc5da62f30512dc83146ed83dd6212db72404","tid":615761,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"快D快D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"等多9秒都心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a8db2af4f8dfeb08f88c7edf43dc35550fedb5","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"千雪完美收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b506089d06166d06ef7ca35bf462eea0276d4d","tid":615761,"uid":56624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46a8db2af4f8dfeb08f88c7edf43dc35550fedb5","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"千雪完美收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"點同結衣鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e625abc312affc859380428059163a73dbee27b","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27b506089d06166d06ef7ca35bf462eea0276d4d","tid":615761,"uid":56624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46a8db2af4f8dfeb08f88c7edf43dc35550fedb5","tid":615761,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"千雪完美收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"點同結衣鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"終於破到蛋，算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\